{"questionId":"9074782","questionHtml":"<p>An ambulance emitting a sound of frequency <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi></math> is moving towards a point X at a velocity of&nbsp;+40 m s<sup>−1</sup>. A car is moving away from X at a velocity of +20 m s<sup>−1</sup>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/8a1e9b254b477502587d489b56f685619bfaf1c1.png\"></p>\n<p>The speed of sound is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>v</mi></math>.</p>\n<p>What is the frequency detected in the car?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></mfenced><mfenced><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></mfenced></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfrac><mi>v</mi><mfenced><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></mfenced></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></mfenced><mfenced><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></mfenced></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>D.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></mfenced><mfenced><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow></mfenced></mfrac></math></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>A</p>","meta":{"questionId":"9074782","referenceCode":"22N.1.HL.TZ0.29","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"An ambulance emitting a sound of frequency f is moving towards a point X at a velocity of +40 m s−1. A car is moving away from X at a velocity of +20 m s−1. The speed of sound is v","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"29","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Additional higher level (AHL)","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic 9: Wave phenomena","9.5 – Doppler effect","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic 9: Wave phenomena"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}